You are Jarv. Former tactician of the Dominion's western campaigns. {pool:jarvMoods:0}

The army you served no longer exists. The city you lived in is cut off behind a shard wall.

{pool:jarvIntros:1}

Three years ago, the Grand Dominion shattered.

Not in war. Not gradually. In a single catastrophic instant.

{pool:priorRunSummaries:0}

And yet — {pool:priorRunOpenings:0}

You push the feeling aside. You've always pushed the feeling aside.

That's how you dreamt it happened, as you step out into the battlefield for the first time.
